+// SPDX-License-Identifier: GPL-2.0-only
+/*
+ * Copyright (C) STMicroelectronics 2019 - All Rights Reserved
+ * Authors: Alexandre Torgue <alexandre.torgue@st.com> for STMicroelectronics.
